{"tid":513121,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"謝霆鋒失戀五部曲先係真正既經典","createTime":"2017-12-29T08:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T09:18:36.000Z","uid":46642,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d6adac7e4c9af586534073188f947c1790a2eeac","tid":513121,"uid":46642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:17:26.000Z","msg":"1. 玉蝴蝶 (作詞：林夕)<br />\n<br />\n我叫你玉蝴蝶　你說這聲音可像你<br />\n戀生花也是你　風之紗也是你　怎稱呼也在這個世界尋獲你<br />\n你哪裡是蝴蝶　然而飛不飛一樣美<br />\n夫斯基也像你　早優生更像你　這稱呼配合你才迴腸和蕩氣<br />\n改得多麼入戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9viavzAf20o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9viavzAf20o&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YvecPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=079da197\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9viavzAf20o</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 非走不可 (作詞：林夕)<br />\n<br />\n也許相戀這條路　擠迫的懷抱　不夠讓我高攀進內才摔倒<br />\n踏上分手這條路　才令我突然看到　你的天空宇宙只夠我流淚　不可跳舞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d7xRE0VkZXE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd7xRE0VkZXE&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YvecPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=702f9a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d7xRE0VkZXE</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 愛後餘生 (作詞：林夕)<br />\n<br />\n假使當初可以為了你　忘了愛所有人<br />\n分開手去追尋　足可擁抱千萬人<br />\n即使天空海闊沒有愛　還有你這個人<br />\n燒光一個森林　將灰燼裡的熱能<br />\n當做一點陪襯 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F-_VUyi8T50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DF-_VUyi8T50&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YvecPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=7be7286d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F-_VUyi8T50</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 邊走邊愛 (作詞：林夕)<br />\n<br />\n每次我其實都想告訴你好不好棲息在快樂園地<br />\n只可惜風太大你太快　還是我在路上遺留下自己<br />\n這一生多僥倖趕上過你　偏不知終點時你在何地<br />\n感激這幾里路我與你纏在一起　到別離<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dZhi-fKXtYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdZhi-fKXtYk&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YvecPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=522e75b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dZhi-fKXtYk</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 遊樂場 (作詞：林夕)<br />\n<br />\n最繽紛的花園遊樂過　但求動心<br />\n就算是世間末日　撫心自問　都想秒秒驚心<br />\n最寬廣的公園遊樂過　為何認真<br />\n若我尚佔一席位　都想入座　觀賞這個驚險人生＃<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lv7WMpjoIGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlv7WMpjoIGs&d=WEX6p1p09bNIMuynU0YvecPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d5e0af32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lv7WMpjoIGs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五首都係夕爺作品，單單係失戀一個環節已經有咁多情感，由自覺配唔起對方，到分手既傷痛，到最後迫自己放開，描寫細膩到極點，失戀時聽晒五首就最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nJuno個啲唔該行埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3933ee1c48efcf6f06abd1df35149a80c30fe237","tid":513121,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"五首都好鍾意"},{"pid":"50cb70b309cc2c975f1e5c81f95c74345741b44b","tid":513121,"uid":139228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"你知唔知玉蝴蝶講緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關失戀乜事<br />\n<br />\n仲有首早知呢？？"},{"pid":"63e84c63f3ec2f30dc8d9706bb71a81c9483b754","tid":513121,"uid":93831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"乜撚都幾部曲<br />\n屌你老母睇下隻歌推出既時序啦<br />\n部你老母咩"},{"pid":"84e3cec09f569247e330132f9126aa33be11bc22","tid":513121,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:04:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cbaf5b33b0301e0e1777f3eab370705e5f8e665","tid":513121,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"玉蝴蝶都計<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主小學畢業未？<br />\n<br />\n之前訪問林夕，話呢首歌純粹係chef lemon送咗盤花俾佢，於是佢就寫返首詞當回禮"},{"pid":"83e802b756dd942c3a985ad204d77125bc1391bd","tid":513121,"uid":23495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:18:36.000Z","msg":"玉蝴蝶🦋點睇都唔係失戀歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}